cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.Medical Imaging, cs.NE 

The paper deals with deep learning approaches for medical image segmentation, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI). Additionally, the paper specifically focuses on medical imaging (cs.Medical Imaging) and proposes a new label fusion strategy for multi-atlas segmentation (MAS), which is a common technique in medical image analysis. Lastly, the paper mentions the use of a fast DL registration approach, which could fall under the category of neural engineering (cs.NE).
